				<td colspan="2"><span>If you are a level 49+ bard (I found this works great at 65 anyway) tap a pulse or two of Sheild of Songs, I found this to be the best agro-getter in groups besides 4 chant stacking. Once they attack you, use the escape key to target those still attacking. Take a step back, keep remezing. No problems. The push/pull of the songs are a nice way to do it too. Or be puller, bringing 1-2 is far better then staying with casters for manasong (since it's now pulse based anyway) since you gotta stop singing it altogether to deal with adds. 
