			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>It's easy to get caught up in the mentality of thinking you MUST mez every additional mob in the room.  The reality is this: whatever kills all the mobs present fastest without using excessive mana is the best answer.  Sometimes, that means AE slows or DoTs (or both if you have level 62 melody of mischief) and sometimes it means off-tanking.  But sometimes, the only way to preserve healing mana is to mez.  It takes practice and experimentation to know when.</span></td>
